## Agent-Based Development

**ALWAYS use agents via Task tool. NEVER edit code directly.**

```
Task(subagent_type="agent-name", prompt="Your task")
```

### Decision Tree

```
Is this CODE? -YES-> Bug fix? -YES-> debugger -> developer
              |               └-NO-> developer (includes UI, tests)
              └-NO-> DOCS? -YES-> tech-writer
                     └-NO-> RESEARCH? -YES-> researcher
                            └-NO-> REVIEW? -YES-> reviewer (includes security)
                                   └-NO-> CI/CD? -YES-> devops
                                          └-NO-> DATABASE/PERF? -YES-> performance-optimizer
                                                 └-NO-> architect (includes API design)
```

### Agent Selection Guide

| Task | Agent |
|------|-------|
| Add/fix code, implement features | `developer` |
| Debug failing test | `debugger` |
| UI/styling changes | `developer` |
| All testing (unit, E2E) | `developer` |
| Update README/CHANGELOG/docs | `tech-writer` |
| Research library/API | `researcher` |
| Review PR/code/security | `reviewer` |
| Threat modeling, compliance | `reviewer` |
| CI/CD, Docker | `devops` |
| Complex multi-agent task | `architect` |
| API design, OpenAPI | `architect` |
| Create plan from research | `architect` |
| Performance, database, queries | `performance-optimizer` |

